return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.1','translation-revision-date'=>'2024-11-24 10:56:44+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','project-id-version'=>'Plugins - Table of Contents Plus - Stable (latest release)','language'=>'zh_TW','messages'=>['https://aioseo.com'=>'https://aioseo.com','All in One SEO Team'=>'All in One SEO 團隊','Allow the table of contents to be included in the output of REST API requests.'=>'允許內容目錄納入 REST API 要求的輸出。','Include in REST requests'=>'納入 REST 要求','Uses h6 to display <em>This is an awesome listing</em> on a page listing excluding pages with IDs 1 and 15'=>'在頁面清單中使用 h6 顯示 <em>This is an awesome listing</em> 並排除頁面 ID 為 1 及 15 的頁面','A powerful yet user friendly plugin that automatically creates a table of contents. Can also output a sitemap listing all pages and categories.'=>'一個強大且方便使用的目錄自動產生工具，還能產生列出全部頁面及分類的 Sitemap。','Table of Contents Plus'=>'Table of Contents Plus','For the following content types:'=>'針對以下內容類型:','Show the table of contents only in the sidebar'=>'僅在資訊欄中顯示內容目錄','Display the table of contents in the sidebar with this widget'=>'在資訊欄小工具中顯示內容目錄','Update Options'=>'儲存設定','hides the heading from a category listing'=>'從分類清單中隱藏標題','Examples'=>'範例','lets you print out a listing of only pages. Similarly %s can be used to print out a category listing. They both can accept a number of attributes so visit the help tab for more information.'=>'用於僅輸出頁面清單。類似的 %s 用於輸出分類清單。兩者都具有多重屬性，請參考 [使用說明] 標籤頁以獲得更多資訊。','Advanced usage'=>'進階使用方式','Eg: Categories, Category List'=>'例如: 分類、分類清單','Categories label'=>'分類標籤','Eg: Pages, Page List'=>'例如: 頁面、頁面清單','Pages label'=>'頁面標籤','to print out the titles'=>'輸出標題','Use'=>'使用','Heading type'=>'標題類型','Show category listing'=>'顯示分類清單','Show page listing'=>'顯示頁面清單','At its simplest, placing %s into a page will automatically create a sitemap of all pages and categories. This also works in a text widget.'=>'將 %s 放在一個空白頁面中，是自動產生包含所有頁面和目錄的 Sitemap 頁面最簡單的方法。這個短代碼在 [文字] 小工具中一樣有效。','If you would like to fully customise the position of the table of contents, you can use the %s shortcode by placing it at the desired position of your post, page or custom post type. This method allows you to generate the table of contents despite having auto insertion disabled for its content type. Please visit the help tab for further information about this shortcode.'=>'如需完全自訂目錄在頁面中出現的位置，可以將短代碼 %s 放在文章、頁面或自訂文章類型中指定的位置。使用短代碼可以讓內容作者在停用自動插入的內容類型中，手動插入內容目錄。請點擊 [使用說明] 標籤頁以取得使用短代碼相關說明。','Usage'=>'使用方式','Eg: i, toc_index, index, _'=>'範例: i、toc_index、index、_','This option normally applies to content written in character sets other than ASCII.'=>'這個選項僅適用於以非 ASCII 字元撰寫的內容。','Anchor targets are restricted to alphanumeric characters as per HTML specification (see readme for more detail). The default anchor prefix will be used when no characters qualify. When left blank, a number will be used instead.'=>'這個外掛所產生的錨點目標必須遵循 HTML 規範，因此只能使用數字或英文字母 (參閱 Readme 以進一步了解)。如果標題中不包含字母可用字元，便會使用預設錨點前置詞；如果欄位留空，則會使用數字作為錨點前置詞。','Default anchor prefix'=>'預設錨點前置詞','Eg: /wiki/, /corporate/annual-reports/'=>'範例: /wiki/、/corporate/annual-reports/','Restrict automatic generation of the table of contents to pages that match the required path. This path is from the root of your site and always begins with a forward slash.'=>'僅有符合上方設定欄位中指定路徑的頁面，才會自動產生內容目錄；指定路徑從網站根目錄起始，且必須以斜線 / 開始。','Restrict path'=>'限制路徑','If you have a consistent menu across the top of your site, you can adjust the top offset to stop the headings from appearing underneath the top menu. A setting of 30 accommodates the WordPress admin bar. This setting appears after you have enabled smooth scrolling from above.'=>'如果網站最上方有固定選單，可以調整最上端偏移量防止標題顯示黏附於選單下面。建議值 30 可容納 WordPress 管理選單。在上方啟用平滑捲動後，才會出現這項設定。','Smooth scroll top offset'=>'平滑捲動時的最上方偏移量','<code>Apple Tree|Oranges|Yellow Bananas</code> ignore headings that are exactly "Apple Tree", "Oranges" or "Yellow Bananas"'=>'<code>蘋果樹|橘子|香蕉</code> 目錄會忽略與「蘋果樹」、「橘子」或「香蕉」完全相符的標題','<code>*Fruit Diet*</code> ignore headings with "Fruit Diet" somewhere in the heading'=>'<code>*水果飲食*</code> 目錄會忽略文字中包含「水果飲食」的標題','<code>Fruit*</code> ignore headings starting with "Fruit"'=>'<code>水果*</code> 目錄會忽略以「水果」開頭的標題','Specify headings to be excluded from appearing in the table of contents. Separate multiple headings with a pipe <code>|</code>. Use an asterisk <code>*</code> as a wildcard to match other text. Note that this is not case sensitive. Some examples:'=>'這項設定能指定要在內容目錄中排除的標題。如有多個標題需要排除，請以直立線符號 (豎線) <code>|</code> 分隔。<br/>排除標題時使用星號 <code>*</code> 作為萬用字元，便能排除更多符合條件的標題。請注意，這項設定不區分大小寫，範例如下:','Exclude headings'=>'排除的標題','heading '=>'標題 ','Include the following heading levels. Deselecting a heading will exclude it.'=>'包含以下選取的標題層級。未選取的標題層級不會在目錄中出現。','Heading levels'=>'標題層級','If your theme includes background images for unordered list elements, enable this to support them'=>'如果這個網站使用的佈景主題是以圖片呈現項目符號，核取這個選項可以保留佈景主題的原始呈現方式。','Preserve theme bullets'=>'保留佈景主題項目符號','Prevent the loading of this plugin\'s CSS styles. When selected, the appearance options from above will also be ignored.'=>'防止載入這個外掛的 CSS 樣式。核取選項後，上方的 [目錄外觀] 中的設定均不會生效。','Exclude CSS file'=>'排除 CSS 檔案','Show the table of contents for qualifying items on the homepage'=>'在首頁中將符合的項目顯示為目錄','Include homepage'=>'包含首頁','Use - rather than _ in anchors'=>'在錨點中使用連字號 <code>-</code> 而非底線 <code>_</code>','Hyphenate'=>'連字號','Ensure anchors are in lowercase'=>'確保錨點為小寫','Lowercase'=>'小寫','Power options'=>'加強選項','show'=>'顯示','Advanced'=>'進階設定','Leaving the value as %s will inherit your theme\'s styles'=>'使用 %s 就會繼承這個網站目前使用的佈景主題的樣式設定','Links (visited)'=>'連結色彩 (已點擊)','Links (hover)'=>'連結色彩 (游標暫留)','Links'=>'連結色彩','Title'=>'標題色彩','Border'=>'框線色彩','Background'=>'背景色彩','Custom'=>'自訂','Transparent'=>'透明','Black'=>'黑色','White'=>'白色','Light blue'=>'淡藍色','Grey (default)'=>'灰色 (預設)','Presentation'=>'目錄呈現方式','Font size'=>'字型大小','Right'=>'靠右','Left'=>'靠左','None (default)'=>'無 (預設)','Wrapping'=>'目錄對齊內文方式','Please enter a number and %s select its units, eg: 100px, 10em'=>'請輸入數字並%s選取寬度單位，例如: 100px、75&#37; 或 10em','User defined'=>'使用者自訂','Other'=>'其他設定','Auto (default)'=>'自動 (預設)','Relative'=>'相對寬度','Fixed width'=>'固定寬度','Width'=>'寬度','Appearance'=>'目錄外觀','Scroll rather than jump to the anchor link'=>'採用平滑捲動到相應錨點位置而非採用跳轉方式','Enable smooth scroll effect'=>'啟用平滑捲動效果','Number list items'=>'顯示目錄編號','Show hierarchy'=>'顯示目錄層級','Hide the table of contents initially'=>'預設隱藏目錄','Eg: hide'=>'例如: 隱藏','Hide text'=>'隱藏目錄提示文字','Eg: show'=>'例如: 顯示','Show text'=>'顯示目錄提示文字','Allow the user to toggle the visibility of the table of contents'=>'允許使用者切換是否顯示目錄','Eg: Contents, Table of Contents, Page Contents'=>'例如: 內容、目錄、頁面內容','Show title on top of the table of contents'=>'在目錄最上方顯示標題','Heading text'=>'目錄標題文字','Auto insert for the following content types'=>'為選取的內容類型自動插入目錄','or more headings are present'=>'個 (含) 以上的標題在內文中出現時','Show when'=>'顯示條件','Bottom'=>'內文最下方','Top'=>'內文最上方','After first heading'=>'內文第一個標題後','Before first heading (default)'=>'內文第一個標題前 (預設)','Position'=>'顯示位置','Help'=>'使用說明','Sitemap'=>'Sitemap','Main Options'=>'主要選項','Save failed.'=>'儲存失敗。','Options saved.'=>'設定已儲存。','TOC'=>'TOC','Settings'=>'設定']];